                            "category": "Options",
                            "categoryID": 65,
                            "keyword": "Oil/Gas/Mineral Leases",
                            "sectionID": 30,
                            "text": "<ul><li><font color=\"#FF0000\">Multiple Oil, Gas and Mineral Leases&nbsp;were found for the parent property between 1951 and 2007. No oil or gas exploration activities were observed on the subject property at the time of site reconnaissance. Additionally, no oil or gas wells or pipelines are mapped in the area of the subject property. Based on the lack of evidence of any oil or gas activities at the subject property, theses leases are not a recognized environmental condition to the subject property.</font></li></ul>",
