                            "category": "Options",
                            "categoryID": 65,
                            "keyword": "Main",
                            "sectionID": 31,
                            "text": "<p>No specialized knowledge of RECs, HRECs, or other potential environmental concerns were reported by the Client.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>No property valuation reduction relating to environmental concerns was reported by the Client.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><font color=\"#ff0000\">Mr. Kevin Dugan, representative with KD Dugan &amp; Co, stated he is not aware of any environmental liens that are filed or recorded against the property, nor any deed restrictions, engineering or institutional controls, or other activity and use limitations that are in place or have been filed against the property. In addition, Mr. Dugan stated he does not possess any actual or specialized knowledge or experience that is material to any potential RECs or is aware of any commonly known or reasonably ascertainable information that is material to any potential RECs. Mr. Dugan is not aware of any pending, threatened, or past litigation, any pending, threatened, or past administrative proceedings, or any notices from any governmental entity regarding possible violation of environmental laws relevant to hazardous substances or petroleum products. A copy of the User Questionnaire is provided in Appendix H, Interview Documentation.</font></p>",
