                            "sectionID": 66,
                            "text": "<p> <font color=\"#ff0000\">No suspected microbial growth, water damage, or conditions conducive to mold growth was observed or sampled in areas likely to be disturbed by construction and installation at the time of the site reconnaissance.</font> </p>",
