                            "text": "*****This section needs some language**********-&gt; Check default language menu for options&nbsp;<br><br>*If there is a database hit, import the listing into a table and fill out.<br><br>If there are no hits, after you fill in this section, uncheck the \"Include in Report\" box next to the Summary heading below.",
                            "showInPage": true,
                            "sectionGUID": "9bc241e3-dd48-11e5-b5c1-0e29ed3d2a45",
