                            "sectionID": 101,
                            "text": "\n<font color=\"#ff0000\">One LPST facility, two UST facilities, and one FINDS facility were</font> identified within the prescribed search distance on the EDR environmental database report.\n\n\n\n\n",
                            "showInPage": false,
                            "sectionGUID": "9bc241e3-dd48-11e5-b5c1-0e29ed3d2a45",
